rites `taskId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"81408656-0517-1d71-665a-971d24d7d9a1","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Task"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.taskId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Check Calendar Availability · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"0de4a558-3528-b277-13de-b493fba1d51e","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"2568b763-305b-0155-1488-6a5e3771245b","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Check Calendar Availability\n\ngoogleCalendar — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Slot Free? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"075adafd-76a7-b31d-8d37-c5dc238c2e07","name":"Note: Check Calendar Availability"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Slot Free?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $items().length === 0 || !$json.id }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Create Calendar Event · ②→ Propose Alternative Slots","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"bbcd321b-039d-af5a-8d59-12d185786a97","name":"Note: Slot Free?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Create Calendar Event\n\ngoogleCalendar — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Confirmation (Outlook) · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,280],"id":"95903bf3-41ac-6d51-4304-dc791fa615d9","name":"Note: Create Calendar Event"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Confirmation (Outlook)\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hold Until Reminder Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"078c942e-1beb-b27c-7f56-c97c9287f0d7","name":"Note: Send Confirmation (Outlook)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Propose Alternative Slots\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"45c8d5d3-906c-08c3-8306-e5fc3fcba565","name":"Note: Propose Alternative Slots"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Until Reminder Time\n\nPauses 1 hours — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Send Reminder (Outlook)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"b5133f4c-86fc-c3e4-94f5-8d656dfa5fd5","name":"Note: Hold Until Reminder Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Reminder (Outlook)\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"ff1c91b0-c8c6-8036-71cd-7d31ac87129d","name":"Note: Send Reminder (Outlook)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"1d8c46cb-634e-ec04-31f5-cf7da52ff436","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"314f9b24-1ef2-df2a-e285-ea633fee88b4","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"38f72324-5ca2-e6fa-1b31-da547bef5714","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Summarize Run Stats · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"bb97719e-6ebb-9ed3-1735-4ae293dd5aed","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"d41e58ee-aa7c-cb0f-e155-6dfa4b17a5a5","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Outlook · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"0dc42419-4341-46c0-5db3-2bb53c554db0","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"a414713f-88ce-05bc-959f-dc6748ecb960","name":"Note: Send Summary to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,1540],"id":"99135e44-cd90-0703-7e88-719f7b76c20b","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,1540],"id":"1d8be8d3-61b9-a6da-cb66-fc5c89fcafba","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,1540],"id":"a060a339-0622-39e1-1ed5-46116a6a8f70","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Provision new customers with Jira and Outlook with instant alerts\n\n**Pattern:** Onboarding Sequence · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nProvision new customers with Jira and Outlook with instant alerts. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual task routing is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Stamp & Shape Task → Payload Valid? → Check Calendar Availability → Slot Free? → Create Calendar Event → Send Confirmation (Outlook) → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to onboarding sequence without manual effort\n- Anyone automating task routing in software development\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"e1872a1b-2b7a-fa52-c2c8-b5ee619f2427","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"e8e32bb8-4639-f67f-f885-274da050fda5","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"e7330d2a-b127-be0d-7534-80d798387ca4","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"d3553111-e71e-f3ef-7433-51bb850a13c2","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your task routing process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"876f8fae-dcf2-d72f-75ba-12ca649c2241","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Task","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Task":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Check Calendar Availability","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Check Calendar Availability":{"main":[[{"node":"Slot Free?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Slot Free?":{"main":[[{"node":"Create Calendar Event","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Propose Alternative Slots","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Create Calendar Event":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Confirmation (Outlook)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Confirmation (Outlook)":{"main":[[{"node":"Hold Until Reminder Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold Until Reminder Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Reminder (Outlook)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Reminder (Outlook)":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Propose Alternative Slots":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Outlook":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"80e1c921-1e91-4ff6-93bc-0dfa34e40f1c","id":"FDX08572"}